name: Lesly - Printable Wedding Invitation Suite
description:
This is a listing for PRINTABLE PDF files of our Lesly Wedding Invitation Suite. The invitations are customized with your information. You can use the sample wording shown, or substitute your own wording. 

Full collection includes:
1. 6.5” x 4.5” Invitation
2. 4.75” x 4.25” Insert #1
3. 5.75” x 4.25” Insert #2
4. 6.75” x 4.25” Insert #2

PROCESS:

1:: PURCHASE. Please include your wedding details during the ordering process, including both your invitation wording and response card wording along with any color changes.

2:: PROOF. Once we receive your information, we will start working on your order. A digital proof will then be sent to you within 2-5 business days of receiving the information for your review. Email any changes** or corrections to us. After all revisions are completed, you will receive a final PDF proof with a request for approval. To approve your order, simply reply to our email and add the word “APPROVED” to the subject line of the email. 

3:: PRINT. Once you approve your order, final files will be sent to you via email. You can have these printed at your local printer (Staples, Kinkos, Office Depot), online printer (Vistaprint, Uprinting) or on your home printer! 

*If you would like other coordinating accessories such as table numbers, escort cards, and menu cards are available. Please convo us to set up a custom listing.

**Please note that two rounds of changes are included with your order. There will be a $10 charge for each additional round of changes.

Adobe Reader is needed to open the PDF file. Download for free at http://get.adobe.com/reader
